---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Author">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About the Author</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_300px] md:items-start">
      <div class="text-neutral-800">
        <p>
          I spent my career of over 37 years in technology, most of that time as a Chief Technology Officer and most recently as Chief Technology and AI leader.
          I retired in March of 2021 and have channeled my love of technology and my global travel into two techno-thrillers, <em>The Quantum Contingent</em>, and <em>Quantum Time</em>.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4">
          Follow along on my journey via my blog, and feel free to ask questions about the books, or the technology within, by replying to the blogs.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4">
          I am blessed to have two wonderful adult children and a lifelong love, Karen. They have all supported me in the creation of these novels.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-6 font-medium">Happy Reading, Greg</p>

        <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-5 text-sm">
          <p class="font-semibold">Links</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 grid gap-2">
            <li><a class="underline" href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/Gregory-R-Simpson/author/B09SNHJ34V" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Amazon Author Page</a></li>
            <li><a class="underline" href="https://www.cio.com/article/221655/the-societal-impact-of-ai.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">CIO.com: The societal impact of AI</a></li>
            <li><a class="underline" href="https://www.ted.com/talks/greg_simpson_merging_humanity_and_the_machine" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">TED talk: Merging humanity and the machine</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="space-y-4">
        <img class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200" src="/images/author/img-0369.jpeg" alt="Gregory R. Simpson" loading="lazy" />
        <img class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200" src="/images/author/africa-930.jpg" alt="On location" loading="lazy" />
        <img class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200" src="/images/author/australia-iphone-1146.jpg" alt="On location" loading="lazy" />
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
